about.description:
Core Library for Google Client Libraries
-------------------------

This package does not include the grpc, grpcio-gcp or grpcgcp extra requirements.

This library is not meant to stand-alone. Instead it defines
common helpers used by all Google API clients. For more information, see the
[documentation](https://googleapis.dev/python/google-api-core/latest/index.html).

Supported Python Versions
-------------------------
Python >= 3.5

Deprecated Python Versions
--------------------------
Python == 2.7
- Python 2.7 support will be removed on January 1, 2020.
- protobuf does not support Visual C++ 2008, windows py27 package not available
about.summary: Core Library for Google Client Libraries

name: google-api-core-split
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "google-api-core" %}
{% set version = "1.17.0" %}
{% set sha256 = "e4082a0b479dc2dee2f8d7b80ea8b5d0184885b773caab15ab1836277a01d689" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}-split
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: {{ sha256 }}

build:
  number: 0
  skip: true  # [win and vc<14]

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip >=18.1
    - setuptools >=34.0.0

outputs:
  - name: {{ name }}
    build:
      script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed --verbose
      skip: true  # [win and vc<14]
    requirements:
      host:
        - python
        - pip >=18.1
        - setuptools >=34.0.0
      run:
        - python
        - futures >=3.2.0  # [py27]
        - google-auth >=1.14.0,<2.0.0dev
        - googleapis-common-protos >=1.6.0,<2.0dev
        - protobuf >=3.4.0
        - pytz
        - requests >=2.18.0,<3.0.0dev
        - setuptools >=34.0.0
        - six >=1.10.0
    test:
      imports:
        - concurrent.futures
        - google.auth
        - google.auth.credentials
        - google.auth.transport.requests
        - google.longrunning
        - google.longrunning.operations_pb2
        - google.protobuf
        - google.rpc
        - platform
        - pytz
        - requests
        - setuptools
        - six
        - six.moves
        - six.moves.urllib.parse
        - google.api_core
        - google.api_core.exceptions
        - google.api_core.future
        - google.api_core.future.base
        - google.api_core.future.polling
        - google.api_core.general_helpers
        - google.api_core.page_iterator
        - google.api_core.protobuf_helpers
        - google.api_core.retry
        - google.api_core.timeout

  - name: {{ name }}-grpc
    build:
      skip: true  # [win and vc<14]
    requirements:
      host:
        - python
        - grpcio >=1.8.2,<2.0dev
      run:
        - {{ pin_subpackage(name, min_pin='x.x', max_pin='x.x') }}
        - grpcio >=1.8.2
    test:
      imports:
        - concurrent.futures
        - google.api_core
        - google.api_core.exceptions
        - google.api_core.future
        - google.api_core.future.base
        - google.api_core.future.polling
        - google.api_core.gapic_v1
        - google.api_core.gapic_v1.client_info
        - google.api_core.gapic_v1.config
        - google.api_core.gapic_v1.method
        - google.api_core.gapic_v1.routing_header
        - google.api_core.general_helpers
        - google.api_core.grpc_helpers
        - google.api_core.operations_v1
        - google.api_core.operations_v1.operations_client
        - google.api_core.page_iterator
        - google.api_core.protobuf_helpers
        - google.api_core.retry
        - google.api_core.timeout
        - google.auth
        - google.auth.credentials
        - google.auth.transport.grpc
        - google.auth.transport.requests
        - google.longrunning
        - google.longrunning.operations_pb2
        - google.protobuf
        - google.rpc
        - grpc
        - platform
        - pytz
        - six
        - six.moves
        - six.moves.urllib.parse
    about:
      home: https://github.com/googleapis/python-api-core
      license: Apache-2.0
      license_family: APACHE
      summary: Core Library for Google Client Libraries with grpc
      description: |
        Core Library for Google Client Libraries with grpc
        -------------------------

        {{ name }}-grpc installs {{ name }} and the grpc extra requirements.

        This library is not meant to stand-alone. Instead it defines
        common helpers used by all Google API clients. For more information, see the
        [documentation](https://googleapis.dev/python/google-api-core/latest/index.html).

        Supported Python Versions
        -------------------------
        Python >= 3.5

        Deprecated Python Versions
        --------------------------
        Python == 2.7
        - Python 2.7 support will be removed on January 1, 2020.
        - protobuf does not support Visual C++ 2008, windows py27 package not available

      doc_url: https://googleapis.dev/python/google-api-core/latest/index.html
      dev_url: https://github.com/googleapis/python-api-core

  - name: {{ name }}-grpcio-gcp
    build:
      skip: true  # [win and vc<14]
    requirements:
      host:
        - python
        - grpcio-gcp >=0.2.2
      run:
        - {{ pin_subpackage(name, min_pin='x.x', max_pin='x.x') }}
        - grpcio-gcp
    test:
      imports:
        - concurrent.futures

        - google.api_core.future
        - google.api_core.future.base
        - google.api_core.future.polling
        - google.api_core.gapic_v1
        - google.api_core.gapic_v1.client_info
        - google.api_core.gapic_v1.config
        - google.api_core.gapic_v1.method
        - google.api_core.gapic_v1.routing_header
        - google.api_core.general_helpers

        - google.api_core.operations_v1
        - google.api_core.operations_v1.operations_client
        - google.api_core.page_iterator
        - google.api_core.protobuf_helpers
        - google.api_core.retry
        - google.api_core.timeout
        - google.auth
        - google.auth.credentials
        - google.auth.transport.grpc
        - google.auth.transport.requests
        - google.longrunning
        - google.longrunning.operations_pb2
        - google.protobuf
        - google.rpc
        - grpc
        - grpc_gcp
        - platform
        - pytz
        - six
        - six.moves
        - six.moves.urllib.parse
    about:
      home: https://github.com/googleapis/python-api-core
      license: Apache 2.0
      license_family: APACHE
      summary: Core Library for Google Client Libraries with grpcio-gcp
      description: |

      doc_url: https://googleapis.dev/python/google-api-core/latest/index.html
      dev_url: https://github.com/googleapis/python-api-core

  - name: {{ name }}-grpcgcp
    build:
      skip: true  # [win and vc<14]
    requirements:

        - google.auth.transport.requests
        - google.longrunning

        - google.protobuf
